{"tid":788037,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣宣布斷交不足半小時 大陸與薩爾瓦多建立外交關係","createTime":"2018-08-21T07:12:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-21T07:37:43.000Z","uid":75969,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"ba7d72ed342315507bf50ec1d9ead1dcaa4de53c","tid":788037,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T07:12:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180821/_2018082111460937769.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180821%2F_2018082111460937769.jpg&h=92bea37b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n雙方簽署《中華人民共和國和薩爾瓦多共和國關於建立外交關係的聯合公報》。<br />\n<br />\n台灣的外交部今早宣布，台灣與中美洲國家薩爾瓦多斷交，成為今年第3個斷交國，目前台灣的「邦交國」已降到17個。消息宣布不足半小時，大陸的國務委員兼外交部長王毅，與薩爾瓦多共和國外長卡斯塔內達在北京舉行會談，雙方簽署《中華人民共和國和薩爾瓦多共和國關於建立外交關係的聯合公報》。<br />\n<br />\n王毅與卡斯塔內達在北京舉行會談並簽署《中華人民共和國和薩爾瓦多共和國關於建立外交關系的聯合公報》，公報指兩國根據人民的利益和願望，決定自公報簽署之日起，相互承認並建立大使級外交關係。兩國政府同意在互相尊重主權和領土完整、互不侵犯、互不干涉內政、平等互利、和平共處的原則基礎上發展兩國友好關係。<br />\n<br />\n薩爾瓦多共和國政府承認世界上只有一個中國，中華人民共和國政府是代表全中國的唯一合法政府，台灣是中國領土不可分割的一部分。薩爾瓦多共和國政府即日斷絕同台灣的「外交關係」，並承諾不再同台灣發生任何官方關係，不進行任何官方往來。中華人民共和國政府對薩爾瓦多共和國政府的上述立場表示贊賞。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/796615\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F796615&d=uDtCgsR86EXX3RESjWIgBnadZns4eLIrfSaUqUvMaEw%3D&h=7ff1d792\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F796615&h=b4a695f6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/796615</a>"},{"pid":"2a096be661ab94c337b45f63cc9e5cd4330194f5","tid":788037,"uid":104443,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T07:14:42.000Z","msg":"史瓦帝尼<br />\n帛琉<br />\n<br />\n呢兩個應該係中華民國最講義氣嘅邦交國"},{"pid":"8453207d0fa05c5ce1aa95dd6f23bac442ad206f","tid":788037,"uid":170249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T07:16:26.000Z","msg":"贏面輸錢 都叫做贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f04cfc360fda6efa7bfadd84163d51c4407523b1","tid":788037,"uid":183302,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T07:21:51.000Z","msg":"唔緊要 台仔仲有美國佬"},{"pid":"2d940ee8c62b8e5deede53084bd6db01a1e36f21","tid":788037,"uid":144626,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T07:23:56.000Z","msg":"留名睇個政府等畀美國佬推翻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03034b683523aeb9e6f562ec7682de04168536c8","tid":788037,"uid":17866,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T07:28:42.000Z","msg":"算啦....爭埋第三世界既垃圾邦交國做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d047f0cf152cafdea27ef2ea5b909ba706227c5e","tid":788037,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T07:31:48.000Z","msg":"王毅好撚似林青霞"},{"pid":"02429423a8c91eab320d56c3897272e0c4bef24a","tid":788037,"uid":129111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T07:31:59.000Z","msg":"好似中小學啲豬扒埋唔到堆揾返啲戇尻豬扒毒撚玩咁"},{"pid":"c64bff494e76fe8485dd61a28e76dfaeac94147d","tid":788037,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T07:36:36.000Z","msg":"有美國就夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd5cee0dd6cde5c6cc0e6567b195000571fb64dc","tid":788037,"uid":17103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T07:37:43.000Z","msg":"王毅屌你退休去荷利活演奧斯卡啦"}]}